query: SELECT id, tenant_id, kind, labels, props, created_at, updated_at, created_by FROM entities WHERE tenant_id=$1 AND kind=$2 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT $3

SELECT id, tenant_id, kind, labels, props, created_at, updated_at, created_by FROM entities WHERE id = ANY(ARRAY(SELECT id FROM entities WHERE tenant_id=$1 ORDER BY random() LIMIT $2)) AND tenant_id=$3

SELECT id, tenant_id, src_id, dst_id, type, props, created_at, updated_at, created_by FROM relationships WHERE tenant_id=$1 AND src_id = (SELECT id FROM entities WHERE tenant_id=$2 ORDER BY random() LIMIT $3) ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT $4
